OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCentral Belt
OL,6,Fand south will have a dry evening and
OL,7,Fnight. Occasional rain across Argyll,
OL,8,Fthis becoming more persistent along
OL,9,Fthe west coast later. Windy across
OL,10,Fcoastal Argyll.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FRain will spread east
OL,13,Fthrough the day. Becoming drier across
OL,14,FArgyll in the afternoon, and elsewhere
OL,15,Fthrough the evening.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA cold
OL,18,Fstart with some frost on Friday, then
OL,19,Fa dry and sunny day, Dry and bright on
OL,20,FSaturday, clouding over later. Cloudy
OL,21,Fwith a chance of rain on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
